ing insects, returning to the same exposed perch. This is a conspicuous species, with an incessant loud whip call, and repetitive fred-reek-fear song. It will defend the nest aggressively against larger species, including the emerald toucanet. References Stiles and Skutch, A guide to the birds of Costa Rica, ISBN 0-8014-9600-4", "shortSummary": "The dark pewee (Contopus lugubris) is a small passerine bird in the tyrant flycatcher family. It is endemic to the Talamancan montane fores…", "imageUrl": "https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/1/15/Contopus_lugubris.jpg/960px-Contopus_lugubris.jpg", "kingdomId": "taxonomy-kingdom-animalia", "phylumId": "taxonomy-phylum-chordata", "classId": "taxonomy-class-aves", "genusId": "taxonomy-genus-contopus", "speciesId": "taxonomy-species-contopus-lugubris", "taxonomyIds": {"kingdom": "taxonomy-kingdom-animalia", "phylum": "taxonomy-phylum-chordata", "class": "taxonomy-class-aves", "genus": "taxonomy-genus-contopus", "species": "taxonomy-species-contopus-lugubris"}, "expandable": true, "x": 166.98, "y": 487.65, "z": 654.28}, {"id": "taxonomy-species-contopus-lugubris", "name": "Dark pewee", "latinName": "Contopus lugubris", "type": "taxonomy", "taxonomyLevel": "species", "summary": "Dark pewee（Contopus lugubris）是图谱中的分类级分类节点，当前关联1种鸟类，如Dark pewee。", "expandable": true, "memberCount": 1, "x": 166.98, "y": 487.65, "z": 649.14}], "links": [{"key": "bird-dark-pewee-7a7a96fd__belongs_to_species__taxonomy-species-contopus-lugubris", "source": "bird-dark-pewee-7a7a96fd", "target": "taxonomy-species-contopus-lugubris", "relation": "belongs_to_species", "label": "属于种", "evidence": "依据 birds.csv 中的种字段补充。"}, {"key": "taxonomy-species-contopus-lugubris__belongs_to_genus__taxonomy-genus-contopus", "source": "taxonomy-species-contopus-lugubris", "target": "taxonomy-genus-contopus", "relation": "belongs_to_genus", "label": "属于属", "evidence": "依据 birds.csv 分类字段补充：Dark pewee 属于属 Contopus。"}]}
